.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-14::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: camping, dancing, magic-tricks, skydiving
There are 4 different nationalities: australian, indian, indonesian, japanese
4 different games are played: chess, scrabble, go, bridge
1. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is in an even position##4
2. the person who's hobby is dancing is between the person who's hobby is skydiving and the person playing chess##2
3. the person playing scrabble is on the far left or far right##3
4. the person who's hobby is skydiving is in an even position##4
5. the person playing chess is on the right of the person playing go##1
6. the japanese is between the person playing chess and the australian##2
7. the person playing scrabble is on the far right##1
8. the indian is in an even position##4
9. the person playing chess is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2       |    3     |     4      |
| Hobby         | camping    | magic-tricks | dancing  | skydiving  |
| Nationality   | indonesian | indian       | japanese | australian |
| Game         | go   | chess      | bridge | scrabble       |

