2. the person who's hobby is baking is the person drinking almond-milk##1
3. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left of the person watching mystery movies##1
4. the person drinking cola is the person watching superhero movies##1
5. the person drinking cola is on the far left##1
6. the person watching family movies is the person who's hobby is baking##1
7. the person who's hobby is camping is on the left of the person drinking tea##1
8. the person who's hobby is video-games is the person drinking tea##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |    3    |   4    |
| Beverage      | cola      | almond-milk | 7up     | tea    |
| Movie-Genre   | superhero | family      | mystery | satire |
| Hobby           | reading   | baking  | camping     | video-games |

