.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-16::.
4 different pets are kept: lizard, rabbit, mouse, snake
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: baseball, surfing, swimming, water-polo
The people use 4 different means of transport: airplane, bike, car, snowmobile
1. the owner of the lizard is on the left or right of the owner of the rabbit##3
2. the person who's sport is baseball is in an even position##4
3. the person driving the snowmobile is on the far left##1
4. the person who's sport is surfing is on the left or right of the owner of the snake##3
5. the owner of the rabbit is between the person driving the bike and the person who's sport is swimming##2
6. the person driving the airplane is the person who's sport is water-polo##1
7. the owner of the rabbit is on the left of the owner of the lizard##1
8. the person who's sport is baseball is on the left of the owner of the lizard##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |    2     |    3    |     4      |
| Pet    | mouse    | rabbit     | lizard    | snake        |
| Sport       | swimming   | baseball | surfing | water-polo |
| Transport   | snowmobile | car      | bike    | airplane   |

