3. the fan of d&b is on the far left##1
4. the fan of d&b is on the left of the fan of jazz##1
5. the person watching adventure movies is the farmhouse house##1
6. the fan of indie is on the right of the cape-cod house##1
7. the cape-cod house is on the right of the person watching zombie movies##1
8. the fan of d&b is on the left of the person watching satire movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2    |     3     |    4     |
